            <p>In the meantime I also upskilled myself in <strong>Data Science</strong> and worked with Data Analysis, Machine Learning and Data Engineering. Although Iâ€™m stunned by the possibilies of this field, Iâ€™m still a classic dev at heart ðŸ˜‰</p>
            <p>As far as engineering goes, I also have good genes thanks to my family. If you need any help with fixing anything at home or with your car - hit me up!</p>
