            <p>I personally believe that teaching should be exclusive to people who enjoy it, ideally love it. Without your own passion and faith in your students it's very unlikely for them to get better and keep up the motivation to grow. For me being a teacher is a passion in itself - I love seeing people think, progress, fail and get up again for another round. There are only a few more satisfying things out there than this.</p>
